        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Nationwide Right To Unionize Act</b></p> <p>This bill provides authorization for labor agreements to require membership in a labor organization as a condition of employment regardless of state law (thus preempting state laws that prohibit such agreements).</p>]]></text>
